tchburg, Clinton, Sterling, Bolton, Hudson, Berlin, Harvard, Marlborough, Stow, Boxborough, Acton, Concord, and Sudbury."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What services does Maverick City Builders offer?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Maverick City Builders offers kitchen remodeling, bathroom remodeling, deck building, custom carpentry, interior and exterior painting, home additions, building restoration, water damage restoration, and general contracting for residential and commercial clients."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you offer free estimates?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, Maverick City Builders provides free no-obligation estimates. Call (508) 656-7436 or submit a request at mcitybuilders.com."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Maverick City Builders licensed and insured?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, Maverick City Builders is a fully licensed general contractor in Massachusetts and carries general liability insurance and workers compensation coverage."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How long does a kitchen remodel take?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"A typical kitchen remodeling project takes 3 to 6 weeks depending on scope, materials, and permits. Maverick City Builders provides a detailed timeline with every free estimate."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How much does a bathroom remodel cost in Central Massachusetts?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Bathroom remodel costs typically range from $8,000 to $35,000 depending on size and scope. Maverick City Builders provides transparent itemized estimates."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What areas does Maverick City Builders serve?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Maverick City Builders is headquartered in Lancaster, MA and serves all of Central Massachusetts including Worcester, Leominster, Fitchburg, Clinton, Sterling, Bolton, Hudson, Berlin, Harvard, Marlborough, Stow, Boxborough, Acton, Concord, and Sudbury."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I get started?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Call Maverick City Builders at (508) 656-7436 or fill out the contact form at mcitybuilders.com. We will schedule a free consultation and provide a detailed estimate at no cost."}}]}</script><section class="mcb-parallax w-full flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden h-[100svh]" style="background-image: url(&quot;https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://vibe.filesafe.space/1776285954741479289/attachments/cff31d1d-6e8e-4c38-812b-b53a5ff6b705.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=70&amp;output=webp&quot;);"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/80 via-black/60 to-black/90 z-[1] pointer-events-none"></div><div class="container relative z-[2] flex flex-col items-center text-center px-4 animate-in fade-in duration-1000 slide-in-from-bottom-8"><h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto text-white drop-shadow-[0_2px_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]">Home Remodeling Contractor in Lancaster, MA</h1><p class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto font-light tracking-wide drop-shadow-[0_2px_5px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]">Built with precision. Designed to last. Serving Lancaster, Sterling, Clinton, Bolton, Hudson, Berlin, and Worcester County.</p><p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed drop-shadow-[0_2px_5px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]">Maverick City Builders — known locally as MCB — is a Lancaster-based general contractor serving Worcester County, Massachusetts, and surrounding Central MA towns.</p><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center"><a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 h-11 w-fu